      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-maintained, making it a reliable choice for its next owner. The exterior is clean with a great shine, though you may find a few minor stone chips or light surface scratches typical of careful regular use. Inside, the upholstery is in great shape and all interior features, including the infotainment and climate control systems, are fully operational. Mechanically, the car drives smoothly with a responsive engine and a solid suspension, offering a dependable and comfortable driving experience.",
