    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic opportunity for a buyer seeking a well-maintained, reliable driver. The exterior paint retains a deep shine, showing only the minor, expected signs of careful road use, while the body remains straight and free of major blemishes. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean; the seats are supportive and free of tears, and all interior electronics\u2014including the premium audio system and climate control\u2014operate perfectly. Mechanically, this car is in its prime. It has been serviced regularly, with a smooth-shifting transmission and a responsive engine that provides a quiet, confident ride. The tires have plenty of tread remaining, and the brakes feel firm and reliable. Whether you are commuting or heading out on a road trip, this car offers a comfortable, worry-free experience and reflects the pride of its previous ownership.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
